org.apache.juddi.validation

Class ValidatePublish

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.juddi.validation.ValidateUDDIApi
      • org.apache.juddi.validation.ValidatePublish

  • public class ValidatePublish
extends ValidateUDDIApi
    Provides validation of publish requests to Juddi
    Author:
    Jeff Faath, Tom Cunningham, Alex O'Ree Modified March 2013 to validate string length and ref integrity Advisory, be careful calling AppConfig.getConfiguration() from within validation functions, it may inadvertently cause infinite loops during the Install phase
    See Also:
    Install
